title: An Odd Body - Crime Drama
description:
4 X 45 mins

DI Gwen Danbury works for the mythical East Suffolk Police, investigating murders and other serious crimes. Her job would be so much easier though if her mother would not insist on interfering and trying to investigate Gwen's cases herself - as well as criticising Gwen's weight problems.

Each story is self contained, with just the right balance of humour and crime drama.
